And consider the whole edge
of the swamp,

25:05.670 --> 25:06.995
the eastern edge of the swamp,

25:07.080 --> 25:08.589
<i>as having high potential</i>

25:08.748 --> 25:10.257
<i>for containing more artifacts.</i>

25:12.677 --> 25:15.679
I'm gonna take the ceramic
back to the archaeology trailer

25:15.764 --> 25:17.765
- and let Rick know.
