<i>and their partner Craig Tester</i>

25:46.119 --> 25:49.213
<i>to discuss the possible
indigenous pottery</i>

25:49.297 --> 25:51.957
<i>that was discovered near
the mysterious stone feature</i>

25:52.050 --> 25:54.543
<i>in the southeast corner
of the swamp.</i>

