One of the things that
is significantly different

25:57.806 --> 25:59.131
this year than last is

25:59.224 --> 26:01.383
<i>the new regulations that
have come down from</i>

26:01.467 --> 26:03.468
<i>Communities, Culture
and Heritage.</i>

26:03.562 --> 26:06.230
<i>Laird made a significant find
of pottery</i>

26:06.389 --> 26:08.223
<i>in the southeast corner
of the swamp.</i>

